                            <comment id="17492665" author="mkl" created="Tue, 15 Feb 2022 15:05:12 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Can the SigFlags in /Catalog object be removed or its value be changed to 0 so this corresponds to the content of the document ?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;SigFlags&lt;/b&gt; in the &lt;b&gt;Catalog&lt;/b&gt; are meaningless. The relevant &lt;b&gt;SigFlags&lt;/b&gt; entry is the one in the interactive form dictionary, i.e. in the &lt;b&gt;AcroForm&lt;/b&gt; dictionary in the &lt;b&gt;Catalog&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17492771" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 15 Feb 2022 18:15:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1898110 from Tilman Hausherr in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
