&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-5377&quot; title=&quot;pDAcroForm.flatten() does not remove /SigFlags in /Catalog object&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-5377&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-5377&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: remove sigFlags when there is no signature, as suggested by Stefan Geelen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
